msgid "Calculate monthly mortgage payments with taxes, insurance, and PMI"
msgstr "Vergiler, sigorta ve PMI ile aylık ipotek ödemelerini hesaplayın"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:43
msgid "What is included in a monthly mortgage payment?"
msgstr "Aylık ipotek ödemesine neler dahildir?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:46
msgid ""
"A monthly mortgage payment typically includes Principal (loan amount), "
"Interest, Property Taxes, Homeowners Insurance (PITI), and sometimes PMI and"
" HOA fees."
msgstr ""
"Aylık ipotek ödemesi genellikle Anapara (kredi tutarı), Faiz, Emlak "
"Vergileri, Ev Sahibi Sigortası (PITI) ve bazen PMI ve HOA ücretlerini "
"içerir."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:51
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:481
msgid "What is PMI and when is it required?"
msgstr "PMI nedir ve ne zaman gereklidir?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:54
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Private Mortgage Insurance (PMI) is typically required when your down "
"payment is less than 20%% of the home price. PMI protects the lender if you "
"default on the loan."
msgstr ""
"Özel Mortgage Sigortası (PMI), genellikle peşinatınızın ev fiyatının "
"%%20'sinden az olması durumunda gereklidir. PMI, krediyi temerrüde "
"düşürmeniz durumunda borç vereni korur."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:59
msgid "How can I lower my monthly mortgage payment?"
msgstr "Aylık ipotek ödememi nasıl azaltabilirim?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:62
msgid ""
"You can lower your payment by: making a larger down payment, choosing a "
"longer loan term, shopping for lower interest rates, or buying a less "
"expensive home."
msgstr ""
"Ödemenizi şu şekilde düşürebilirsiniz: daha büyük bir peşinat ödeyerek, daha"
" uzun bir kredi vadesi seçerek, daha düşük faiz oranları için alışveriş "
"yaparak veya daha ucuz bir ev satın alarak."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:89
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly mortgage payment including principal, interest, "
"taxes, insurance, and PMI."
msgstr ""
"Anapara, faiz, vergiler, sigorta ve PMI dahil aylık ipotek ödemenizi "
"hesaplayın."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:115
