#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:252
msgid "Enter the property price and your deposit."
msgstr "Emlak fiyatını ve depozitonuzu girin."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:253
msgid "Choose the term and annual interest rate."
msgstr "Vadeyi ve yıllık faiz oranını seçin."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:254
msgid "Select repayment or interest-only."
msgstr "Geri ödemeyi veya yalnızca faizi seçin."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:255
msgid "Click Calculate to see the monthly payment and schedule."
msgstr "Aylık ödemeyi ve planı görmek için Hesapla'yı tıklayın."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:260
msgid "What is LTV?"
msgstr "LTV nedir?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:262
msgid ""
"Loan-to-Value (LTV) is the loan amount divided by the property price. A "
"higher deposit reduces LTV and can help you access better rates."
msgstr ""
"Kredi/Değer Oranı (LTV), kredi tutarının mülk fiyatına bölünmesiyle elde "
"edilen değerdir. Daha yüksek bir para yatırma LTV'yi azaltır ve daha iyi "
"oranlara erişmenize yardımcı olabilir."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:269
msgid "Mortgage Formulas"
msgstr "İpotek Formülleri"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:273
msgid "Loan = Property Price − Deposit"
msgstr "Kredi = Emlak Fiyatı − Mevduat"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:276
msgid "Repayment (monthly payment)"
msgstr "Geri ödeme (aylık ödeme)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:280
msgid "Interest-only (monthly payment)"
msgstr "Yalnızca faiz (aylık ödeme)"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator_uk.html:284
msgid ""
"Where P is loan amount, r is monthly interest rate (annual rate ÷ 12), and n"
" is number of months."
msgstr ""
"P'nin kredi tutarı olduğu yerde, r aylık faiz oranıdır (yıllık oran ÷ 12) ve"
" n ay sayısıdır."

