#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:320
msgid "What are Carbohydrates?"
msgstr "Karbonhidratlar nelerdir?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"Carbohydrates are one of the three main macronutrients (along with protein "
"and fat) that provide energy to your body. They are broken down into "
"glucose, which is the primary fuel source for your brain and muscles."
msgstr ""
"Karbonhidratlar, vücudunuza enerji sağlayan üç ana makro besin maddesinden "
"(protein ve yağ ile birlikte) biridir. Beyniniz ve kaslarınız için birincil "
"yakıt kaynağı olan glikoza parçalanırlar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"Carbohydrates provide 4 calories per gram and are found in foods like "
"grains, fruits, vegetables, legumes, and dairy products. They play a crucial"
" role in maintaining energy levels, supporting physical performance, and "
"fueling brain function."
msgstr ""
"Karbonhidratlar gram başına 4 kalori sağlar ve tahıllar, meyveler, sebzeler,"
" baklagiller ve süt ürünleri gibi gıdalarda bulunur. Enerji seviyelerinin "
"korunmasında, fiziksel performansın desteklenmesinde ve beyin fonksiyonunun "
"desteklenmesinde çok önemli bir rol oynarlar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:331
msgid "Types of Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Karbonhidrat Çeşitleri"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:334
msgid "Simple Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Basit Karbonhidratlar"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Quick-digesting carbs found in fruits, milk, and processed foods. Provide "
"rapid energy but can cause blood sugar spikes."
msgstr ""
"Meyvelerde, sütte ve işlenmiş gıdalarda bulunan hızlı sindirilen "
"karbonhidratlar. Hızlı enerji sağlar ancak kan şekerinin aniden yükselmesine"
" neden olabilir."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:338
msgid "Examples: Sugar, honey, fruit juice, white bread"
msgstr "Örnekler: Şeker, bal, meyve suyu, beyaz ekmek"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:341
msgid "Complex Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Kompleks Karbonhidratlar"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Slow-digesting carbs found in whole grains, vegetables, and legumes. Provide"
" sustained energy and are rich in fiber."
msgstr ""
"Tam tahıllarda, sebzelerde ve baklagillerde bulunan yavaş sindirilen "
"karbonhidratlar. Sürekli enerji sağlar ve lif açısından zengindir."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:345
msgid "Examples: Oats, brown rice, quinoa, sweet potatoes, beans"
msgstr "Örnekler: Yulaf, kahverengi pirinç, kinoa, tatlı patates, fasulye"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:348
msgid "Fiber"
msgstr "Elyaf"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:350
msgid ""
"A type of carbohydrate that cannot be digested. Important for digestive "
"health, blood sugar control, and satiety."
msgstr ""
"Sindirilemeyen bir karbonhidrat türüdür. Sindirim sağlığı, kan şekeri "
"kontrolü ve tokluk için önemlidir."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:352
msgid "Examples: Whole grains, vegetables, fruits, legumes"
msgstr "Örnekler: Tam tahıllar, sebzeler, meyveler, baklagiller"

